data.description: Introducing this charming 2-story, 3BR/2.5BA, single-family home on 1.58 acres in Valdese. It is located just 15 minutes to Morgantown, 24 minutes to Hickory, and 25 minutes to Lenoir. As you enter the home from the covered front porch with newly placed trex decking, you'll step into the main living/ dining area as it opens into a beautiful kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a custom island, and a walk-in pantry. The master suite on the main level includes a double-sink vanity as well as a newly re-done glass shower and master closet. The upper level of the home has a split bedroom floor plan that includes a full bathroom. The back deck is accessed from the mudroom and opens up to a newly constructed outdoor patio/firepit area.  Joy all of the convenience of city water, city sewer, wired internet, cable, dual-zoned heating and cooling, and smart remote locks. The outdoor shed is great for additional storage and the covered RV shed has been prewired for a 50AMP connection.
